Package org.coliper.ibean.proxy.handler

IBean internal package that contains all ProxyIBeanFactory related ExtensionHandlers for the predefined extension interfaces. Bean extension interfaces that are predefined in the IBean framework can be found in package org.coliper.ibean.extension. To enable all these interfaces with the proxy implementation of IBean (see org.coliper.ibean.proxy an ExtensionHandler is required for each interface. This package contains all these handlers.
